commit.message:
[OpenACC] handle missing OMP_LIST_ clauses in fortran's parse tree debugger

	gcc/fortran/
	* dump-parse-tree.c (show_omp_clauses): Add missing omp list_types
	and reorder the switch cases to match the enum in gfortran.h.

From-SVN: r264446

files.patch:

+	and reorder the switch cases to match the enum in gfortran.h.
